Interface IAct

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<IAct>
All Known Implementing Classes:
Act
public interface IAct
extends java.lang.Comparable<IAct>

An act is the association of a schema with the feedback the agent receives when trying to enact that schema. The term Act and the term interaction are used indifferently.

Author:
mcohen, ogeorgeon
